criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  gestational age less than 36 weeks;

          -  diagnosis of respiratory distress (RDS);

          -  need for ventilatory support;

          -  written informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  congenital malformations;

          -  genetic disorders;

          -  perinatal asphyxia;

          -  withdrawal of informed consent.
